Distance Education Info: IFHE, The Center for Distance and Online Education is an AICTE approved and Hyderabad based institution which was established 3 decades ago under the umbrella of the ICFAI Foundation for Higher Education. The college is accredited by the NAAC with A++ grade and recognized by the UGC. In addition to this, IFHE is a member of the Association of Commonwealth Universities and the Association of Indian Universities. And the institute is offering an online MBA course of a minimum of 2 years’ duration and a maximum of 4 years’ time at the Postgraduate level with a bequest of 30 years in Management education and 20 years of legacy in distance learning. This distance learning has 22 courses and is particularly designed for working professionals and people who want to make a career in Management. Also, admission to this course is offered based on marks obtained by candidates in last year’s qualifying exam and their performance in Presentations and Personal Interviews.
